data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT - Seller moving only because of job relocation - they LOVE this home and community. This is your chance to buy a newer home in the beautiful community of Ocotillo in Chandler. Ocotillo is known for its green spaces, walking and biking paths, restaurants, shops, top rated schools, and is close to major corporations like Intel. This single level 4 bed, 2.5 bath home is located in the gated community of Enclave at Pinelake! You will love the dark wood look tile floors, white cabinets, granite countertops, gas stove, and kitchen backsplash. Rest better knowing you can still take advantage of the builder warranty, have a brand new AC unit, soft water, RO system, and a new roof! Walk to the community park or ride bikes along the 6.5 mile Paseo Trail path next to the community.
